        <abstract>
            <p>Advice to GHD on whether to accept invitation to lecture at the Royal Institution.</p> 
<p>Murray has sent the <hi rend="italic">Quarterly Review</hi> issue. CD has told Murray that he is convinced Mivart is the author and what he thinks of him.</p> 
        </abstract>
